messages.message: Hey all, File Loading in Annotator, Flow Review, etc. was painfully slow (took more than 60 seconds and then gateway timeout) in my demo to a candidate [between 12:45-1:45pm] on Instabase PROD. We need to take these issues on HIGH priority because these do real damage in candidate demos, customer demos, etc.. Can we have someone look into this please?
We’re redeploying to prod very soon to restore state. @Xi Cheng

We were planning on redeploying at 4pm today - but we can do it earlier if it won’t impact any demos
```I've already had a PR for this, and the current plan is to push this to prod around 4pm PST Oct, 19.```
@Anant Thanks for letting us know. As mentioned by Heymian, I was planning to do the repush around 4pm PST, but can definitely do so now.
